name: The Crypto You
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: The Crypto You is the first Baby Metaverse blockchain game on Binance Smart Chain (BSC). Players can summon characters, complete daily mining missions, conquer the Dark Force, loot rare items to play and earn.
